category: 2 WORDS IN ONE
category comment: 

clue: Cleopatra's cobra plus a command to stop gives us this road surface

response: asphalt (asp + halt)

clue: To ask for spare change plus one ninth of a baseball game gives us this starting place

response: beginning (beg + inning)

clue: One piece of butter plus public group violence gives us this nation lover

response: patriot (pat + riot)

clue: A Catholic religious service plus a standard unit of area gives us this wanton slaughter

response: a massacre (mass + acre)

clue: A shark appendage plus a type of beer gives us this musical conclusion

response: finale (fin + ale)

